 (MUQSE-TO) was engraved on the ring stone of Prophet Suleman (a) by whose blessing and Majesty all the Jinn, human being, animals and birds were obedient to him.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ek qoul hai keh yeh ism (MUQSE-TO) Hazrat Suleman (a) ki angoothi par naqsh tha jis ki barkat o haibat se tamaam jin o ins (jinnaat o insaan) aur charind o parind (jaanwar o parinde) aap (a) ke mutee o farman bardaar thay.", "UrduDescription": "ایک قول ہے کہ یہ اسم حضرت سلمانؑ کی انگوٹھی پر نقش تھا جس کی برکت و ہیبت سے تمام جن و انس اور چرند و پرند آپ کے مطیع و فرمانبردار تھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1021470, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "One who is overpowered by whispering or is suffering from too much wet dream or getting evil thought should write AL-MUQSE-TO on the ball made of wax wrap it and keep with oneself will be protected from such disease.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jis par waswase ghaalib ho ya ziyadah mohtalim (wet dream) hota ho aur be-hudah khayaalaat aate ho to AL-MUQSE-TO ko mom (wax) ke gole par likh kar usey lapet kar apne paas rakkhe to un moozi amraaz (halaak karne waali bimaariyo’n) se najaat paayega.", "UrduDescription": "جس پر وسوسے غالب ہوں یا زیادہ محتلم ہوتا اور بے ہودہ خیالات عارض ہوتے ہوں تو ’’اَلْمُقْسِطُ‘‘ کو مربع شکل میں پر کرکے تازہ اور مستعمل موم میں لپیٹ کر اپنے پاس رکھے تو ان موذی امراض سے نجات پائے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, 